            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.5</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
<p>MergeMole 1.0 is here.</p>
<p>MergeMole lives in your menu bar and shows the GitHub pull requests that actually need you, with AI doing the triage so you always know what to look at first.</p>
<p>In this first release:</p>
<ul>
<li>On-device AI reads each open PR and ranks it by priority and effort, so the ones that matter rise to the top</li>
<li>Every PR gets a plain one line summary of what it does, alongside its review state, checks, and merge status</li>
<li>Everything runs locally on your Mac. It&#x27;s completely free, and your code never leaves your device</li>
<li>Want a different model? Connect your own OpenAI-compatible, Anthropic, or local Ollama endpoint. Prefer no AI? Turn it off and use MergeMole as a fast, clean pull request list</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
